# Password Strength Analyzer

A Python-based cybersecurity project that evaluates the strength of passwords.

## Features
- Password length checking
- Uppercase, lowercase, numbers, and special characters validation
- Password scoring system
- Common password detection
- Password reuse prevention using SQLite
- Password suggestion generator

## Technologies
- Python
- Regex
- SQLite
- Hashlib

## Run
python app.py
python password_generator.py
